des: We are Sapphire Radio based in the beautiful sun filled island of Cyprus. We are a not for profit radio station supporting the community, charities and businesses alike. We aim to enlighten our listeners lives with a great mix of tunes from over the decades - delivered by voices who just love what they do. So, join us whenever you can - at home, at work, in the car, on the beach - anywhere you like! Download our App or go to our website www.sapphireradio.com for instant access, or ask Alexa "alexa play sapphire radio paphos"
